{"ayat_mp3":"https://everyayah.com/data/Alafasy_128kbps/002231.mp3","arabic":"وَإِذَا طَلَّقۡتُمُ ٱلنِّسَآءَ فَبَلَغۡنَ أَجَلَهُنَّ فَأَمۡسِكُوهُنَّ بِمَعۡرُوفٍ أَوۡ سَرِّحُوهُنَّ بِمَعۡرُوفٖۚ وَلَا تُمۡسِكُوهُنَّ ضِرَارٗا لِّتَعۡتَدُواْۚ وَمَن يَفۡعَلۡ ذَٰلِكَ فَقَدۡ ظَلَمَ نَفۡسَهُۥۚ وَلَا تَتَّخِذُوٓاْ ءَايَٰتِ ٱللَّهِ هُزُوٗاۚ وَٱذۡكُرُواْ نِعۡمَتَ ٱللَّهِ عَلَيۡكُمۡ وَمَآ أَنزَلَ عَلَيۡكُم مِّنَ ٱلۡكِتَٰبِ وَٱلۡحِكۡمَةِ يَعِظُكُم بِهِۦۚ وَٱتَّقُواْ ٱللَّهَ وَٱعۡلَمُوٓاْ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ بِكُلِّ شَيۡءٍ عَلِيمٞ","bengali":"আর যখন তোমরা স্ত্রীদেরকে তালাক দিয়ে দাও, অতঃপর তারা নির্ধারিত ইদ্দত সমাপ্ত করে নেয়, তখন তোমরা নিয়ম অনুযায়ী তাদেরকে রেখে দাও অথবা সহানুভুতির সাথে তাদেরকে মুক্ত করে দাও। আর তোমরা তাদেরকে জ্বালাতন ও বাড়াবাড়ি করার উদ্দেশ্যে আটকে রেখো না। আর যারা এমন করবে, নিশ্চয়ই তারা নিজেদেরই ক্ষতি করবে। আর আল্লাহর নির্দেশকে হাস্যকর বিষয়ে পরিণত করো না। আল্লাহর সে অনুগ্রহের কথা স্মরণ কর, যা তোমাদের উপর রয়েছে এবং তাও স্মরণ কর, যে কিতাব ও জ্ঞানের কথা তোমাদের উপর নাযিল করা হয়েছে যার দ্বারা তোমাদেরকে উপদেশ দান করা হয়। আল্লাহকে ভয় কর এবং জেনে রাখ যে, আল্লাহ সর্ববিষয়েই জ্ঞানময়।","english":"And when you have divorced women and they have fulfilled the term of their prescribed period, either take them back on reasonable basis or set them free on reasonable basis. But do not take them back to hurt them, and whoever does that, then he has wronged himself. And treat not the Verses (Laws) of Allah as a jest, but remember Allah's Favours on you (i.e. Islam), and that which He has sent down to you of the Book (i.e. the Quran) and Al-Hikmah (the Prophet's Sunnah - legal ways - Islamic jurisprudence, etc.) whereby He instructs you. And fear Allah, and know that Allah is All-Aware of everything","wbw":[{"bengali":"এবং যখন","english":"And when","en_t":"wa-idha","arabic":"وَإِذَا","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_001.mp3"},{"bengali":"তোমরা তালাক দাও","english":"you divorce","en_t":"tallaqtumu","arabic":"طَلَّقۡتُمُ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_002.mp3"},{"bengali":"স্ত্রীদেরকে","english":"the women","en_t":"al-nisaa","arabic":"ٱلنِّسَآءَ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_003.mp3"},{"bengali":"তারা অতঃপর পৌঁছে","english":"and they reach","en_t":"fabalaghna","arabic":"فَبَلَغۡنَ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_004.mp3"},{"bengali":"তাদের মেয়াদে","english":"their (waiting) term","en_t":"ajalahunna","arabic":"أَجَلَهُنَّ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_005.mp3"},{"bengali":"তাদেরকে রেখে দাও তখন","english":"then retain them","en_t":"fa-amsikuhunna","arabic":"فَأَمۡسِكُوهُنَّ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_006.mp3"},{"bengali":"ন্যায়সঙ্গতভাবে","english":"in a fair manner","en_t":"bima'rufin","arabic":"بِمَعۡرُوفٍ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_007.mp3"},{"bengali":"অথবা","english":"or","en_t":"aw","arabic":"أَوۡ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_008.mp3"},{"bengali":"তাদের মুক্ত করে দাও","english":"release them","en_t":"sarrihuhunna","arabic":"سَرِّحُوهُنَّ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_009.mp3"},{"bengali":"ন্যায় সংগতভাবে","english":"in a fair manner","en_t":"bima'rufin","arabic":"بِمَعۡرُوفٖۚ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_010.mp3"},{"bengali":"এবং না","english":"And (do) not","en_t":"wala","arabic":"وَلَا","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_011.mp3"},{"bengali":"তাদেরকে তোমরা আটকে রেখো","english":"retain them","en_t":"tum'sikuhunna","arabic":"تُمۡسِكُوهُنَّ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_012.mp3"},{"bengali":"ক্ষতির (উদ্দেশ্যে)","english":"(to) hurt","en_t":"diraran","arabic":"ضِرَارٗا","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_013.mp3"},{"bengali":"বাড়াবাড়ি করার জন্যে","english":"so that you transgress","en_t":"lita'tadu","arabic":"لِّتَعۡتَدُواْۚ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_231_014.mp3"},{"bengali":"এবং যে কেউ","english":"And whoeve